      <title>市场关注巴西霜冻风险，咖啡价格五周内涨幅最大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/coffee-jumps-most-in-five-weeks-as-market-eyes-brazil-frost-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于主要生产国巴西部分地区出现轻微霜冻，加剧了人们对供应的担忧，纽约阿拉比卡咖啡价格大幅上涨，交易商估计本周南美国家预计将再次遭遇寒流。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/coffee-jumps-most-in-five-weeks-as-market-eyes-brazil-frost-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 10:35:35 GMT</pubDate>
